description: This is a personal favourite of mine, light and citrusy, with an orange syrup drizzled over the top.
name: Orange Olive Oil Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Use a toothpick or skewer and poke some holes across the top of the cake. Pour the syrup over the cake. Scatter with the toasted pistachios, slice and serve with some whipped cream, ice cream or just as it is with a cuppa. Enjoy.
